  (‚àë i in range k, f i) + (‚àè' i, f (i + k)) = ‚àè' i, f i :=
by simpa only [add_comm] using
  ((has_prod_nat_add_iff k).1 ((multipliable_nat_add_iff k).2 h).has_prod).unique h.has_prod

