/-- If `f‚ÇÄ, f‚ÇÅ, f‚ÇÇ, ...` and `g‚ÇÄ, g‚ÇÅ, g‚ÇÇ, ...` are both convergent then so is the `‚Ñ§`-indexed
sequence: `..., g‚ÇÇ, g‚ÇÅ, g‚ÇÄ, f‚ÇÄ, f‚ÇÅ, f‚ÇÇ, ...`. -/
